                <fr:addr>jms-00IH</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00IH.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="The full relation">The full relation</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Example</fr:taxon>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <html:p>For any two sets <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>, we may form the <html:em><html:strong>full <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7.xml" title="Relation" addr="jms-00I7" type="local">relation</fr:link></html:strong></html:em> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (A\times  B\right )\mathclose {}}\colon  A\mathbin {\nrightarrow } B]]></fr:tex>, also called the <html:em><html:strong>total <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jms-00I7.xml" title="Relation" addr="jms-00I7" type="local">relation</fr:link></html:strong></html:em>, so that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\mathrel {{\mathopen {}\left (A\times  B\right )\mathclose {}}}b]]></fr:tex> for all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[a\in  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b\in  B]]></fr:tex>. In other words, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{\mathopen {}\left (A\times  B\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex> is the <html:em>total</html:em> subset of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A\times  B]]></fr:tex>.</html:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                  <fr:contributor>
                    <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/marcelofiore.xml" title="Marcelo Fiore" addr="marcelofiore" type="local">Marcelo Fiore</fr:link>
                  </fr:contributor>
                </fr:authors>
